{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"removeAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820"}},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","title":"removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}]}}}